Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,色花堂 Tony製作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美幸 看新聞了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.49,0:01:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說那個犯人藏在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.16,0:01:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個犯饒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個逃跑的強姦犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得把門窗鎖好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.04,0:02:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也盡量早點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.44,0:02:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早點回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的連續強姦犯阿久津陸夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人目擊到他曾在這裡出沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方提醒附近居民提高警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是來自現場的播報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.03,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越獄者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多警察啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣反而比較放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看電視了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同期的村瀨生孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該送什麼賀禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩還是女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先問問想要什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都送賀禮的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有重複的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問一問吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.64,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有小孩之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳就會被他搶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.72,0:04:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妳想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.92,0:04:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順其自然吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去旅行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受戀人的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是要關好門窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我也早點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我是誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.63,0:10:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不聽話可饒不了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒碰女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒碰床了
